@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #84398 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
AFAICT, this is valid code no longer compiling. Was there a decision in the PR for this backcompat break, or was it a mistake? P-high if the latter.
Definitely a mistake. That PR should theoretically have had no user-visible changes.
ok let's see an mcve but I would tend to assign a p-high because the issue breaks compiling a project
Go for it. :) I already agree with P-high based on Jack's response.
